### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/decolamos

### List Aircraft
GET http://localhost:8000/aircraft

### Create Aircraft
POST http://localhost:8000/aircraft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "F-16C",
  "manufacturer": "Lockheed Martin",
  "year": 1991
}

### Create Aircraft — edge case: earliest valid year
POST http://localhost:8000/aircraft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "Wright Flyer",
  "manufacturer": "Wright Brothers",
  "year": 1903
}

### Create Aircraft — should fail: year too old
POST http://localhost:8000/aircraft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "Invalid",
  "manufacturer": "Nobody",
  "year": 1800
}

### Create Aircraft — should fail: empty model
POST http://localhost:8000/aircraft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "",
  "manufacturer": "Test",
  "year": 2020
}
